<view class="page-shell"><view class="custom-nav" style="padding-top: {{navTop}}px; height: {{navHeight}}px;"><view class="back-button" bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}" mode="aspectFit" /><text>返回负责人工作台</text></view><text>课程课包</text></view><scroll-view class="page-scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height: {{navSpacer}}px;"></view><view class="content"><view class="page-heading"><text>课程课包</text><text>⌖ 浦东校区⌄</text></view><view class="metric-grid"><view wx:for="{{metrics}}" wx:key="label"><text>{{item.symbol}}</text><text>{{item.label}}</text><text>{{item.value}}</text></view></view><view class="section-title">▤ 课包列表</view><view class="package-card" wx:for="{{packages}}" wx:key="name" bindtap="openPackage"><image src="{{court}}" mode="aspectFill" /><view class="package-copy"><text>{{item.name}}</text><view><text>◷ 课时　{{item.hours}}</text><text>✓ 有效期　{{item.days}}</text><text>♙ 已购人数　{{item.buyers}}</text></view><view><text>适用班型</text><text>{{item.classInfo}}</text></view></view><view class="package-side"><text>￥{{item.price}}</text><text>● 在售</text><text>›</text></view></view><view class="section-title">▱ 课消规则</view><view class="rules-card"><view wx:for="{{rules}}" wx:key="title"><text>{{item.symbol}}</text><view><text>{{item.title}}</text><text>{{item.caption}}</text></view></view></view><button class="primary-button" bindtap="createPackage">＋ 新建课程课包</button><view class="pc-tip">ⓘ 复杂上架配置（价格/赠课/阶梯/权限等）请前往【机构PC端-课程产品】进行管理　›</view><view class="safe-space"></view></view></scroll-view></view>
